Package: ggfunnel
Type: Package
Title: A 'R' package to create 'Power BI' like funnel charts.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pedro Duarte Faria
Maintainer: Pedro Duarte Faria <pedropark99@gmail.com>
Description: 'ggfunnel' uses the 'ggplot2' package to produce
  funnel charts similar to those produced by 'Power BI' tool.
